sequenceDiagram
  participant Browser
  participant LV as TetWeb.SessionLive
  participant API as Tet facade
  participant Runtime as tet_runtime
  participant Bus as Tet.EventBus
  participant Store as Tet.Store adapter

  Browser->>LV: open /sessions/:id
  LV->>API: Tet.get_session(id)
  API->>Runtime: get_session
  Runtime->>Store: load session
  Store-->>Runtime: %Tet.Session{}
  Runtime-->>API: session
  API-->>LV: session
  LV->>API: Tet.list_events(id)
  LV->>API: Tet.subscribe(id)
  Browser->>LV: approve patch
  LV->>API: Tet.approve_patch(session_id, approval_id)
  API->>Runtime: dispatch PatchDecision
  Runtime->>Bus: publish approval/patch/verifier events
  Bus-->>LV: %Tet.Event{}
  LV-->>Browser: render updated state

  Note over LV,Runtime: LiveView renders and calls Tet.* only. No domain logic here.
